text: Beautiful piece of art donated by Jackie Chan himself. One of it is a opera theatre and the other is a double tier pavilion. The structures are well maintained and were somewhat restore over the years since it was made.

Lovely art by Jackie Chan! Really showcases the international ties that SUTD has not only with MIT but with China as well. Amidst the modern design of the campus rises this retro looking structure. A great compliment!
I came here to disown my son and cheat on my wife in Jackie Chan's memory.
Thanks for giving us this art
